Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
Conference (CPPCC) Wu Xueqian met with foreigners who are
attending the Third Conference on Peace, Disarmament, and
Symbiosis in the Asia-Pacific (PDSAP) here today.
</P>
<P>
The non-governmental meeting is attended by 40 persons from ten
countries including China, India, Japan, the Republic of Korea,
Mongolia, Nepal, Pakistan, the Philippines, Russia, and
Vietnam. It opened today and will conclude on Monday.
</P>
