<HEADLINE> Association Set Up to Promote Flower Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, April 19 (Xinhua) -- China Association for the
Promotion of Flower Industry has been set up, Zeng Yuzhuang,
director of the State Bureau for Land Reclamation under the
Ministry of Agriculture, announced here.
</P>
<P>
The association will give a push to the nationwide flower
industry of the land reclamation system, promote the cooperation
between the flower enterprises in various sectors, set up a
national information network, and provide quality seeds to the
flower growers.
</P>
