The land reclamation system, covering the whole country, owns
concentrated areas of arable land. Last year, the land reclamation
system produced more than 500 million pieces of fresh flower, set
up three large-scale wholesale markets and 133 retail outlets, and
reported a total output value of 570 million yuan for the flowers
sector.
</P>
<P>
The association has drawn in 51 members. 
