<HEADLINE> Int'l Women Inventors Conference Closes in Cuba </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAVANA, April 18 (Xinhua) -- The 2rd International Conference
of Women Inventors, focusing on women's role in invention, closed
here today.
</P>
<P>
