Committee and the Steering Committee were yet to be fixed.
</P>
<P>
The Steering Committee, which was expected to meet Friday
night, deferred its sitting in view of the late arrival of the
prime minister and other Front leaders from a funeral held in
Orissa for the deceased veteran leader of Janata Dal, Biju
Patnaik.  
