<HEADLINE> Cuban Olympic President Dies </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAVANA, April 18 (Xinhua) -- Manuel Gonzalez Guerra, president
of the Cuban Olympic Committee, died here on Friday at age 83.
</P>
<P>
